ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Cleave|TYPE:General.Fighter.AttackOption|DESC:If you deal a creature enough damage to make it drop, you get an immediate, extra melee attack against another creature within reach. You can use this ability once per round.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Great Cleave|TYPE:General.Fighter.AttackOption|DESC:This feat works like Cleave, except that there is no limit to the number of times you can use it per round.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Weapon Specialization|APPLIEDTO:Sword (Bastard)|TYPE:Special.Fighter|DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on all damage rolls you make using the selected weapon.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Greater Weapon Focus|APPLIEDTO:Sword (Bastard)|TYPE:General.Fighter|DESC:You gain a +1 bonus on all attack rolls you make using the selected weapon. This bonus stacks with other bonuses on attack rolls, including the one from Weapon Focus.
